<br>
I recently started an ogre warrior, and I have been paying lots of attention to his ac and defence point .<br>
I noticed that sometimes one defence point gives one ac, sometimes 2 , sometimes 3, sometimes even 4.<br>
There doesn't seem to have a consistency........<br>
<br>
I had a iksar monk before, and I noticed that my ac increase is fixed, can anyone tell me how does the warrior ac and defence point works?<br>
<br>
Kinda curious how much ac my ogre warrior would have at lvl 60 with the current gears.....<br>
<br>
Also I know the defence points is caped at 252,so when do we start to get less than 5 points of defence per level? and how many defence point would it be per level after that?<br>
<br>
<br>
Thank you<br>
<br>
